Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)}风云突变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.42,0:00:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,记住 要成为真正的忍者\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Remember, to be a true ninja,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们必须与影子融为一体\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}you must become one with the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗赋予忍者力量\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Darkness gives the ninja power,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.11,0:00:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,而光明会暴露忍者的行踪\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}while light reveals the ninja's presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.47,0:00:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能否熄灭这火焰\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}can you extinguish this flame
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,而不暴露自己?\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}without revealing yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,声音太大 多纳泰罗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Too noisy, Donatello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,太笨拙了 米开朗基罗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Too clumsy, Michelangelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕的选择 拉斐尔\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Poor choice, Raphael.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,干得好 李奥纳多\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Well done, Leonardo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,老师的宠儿\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Teacher's pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,辍学的忍者\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Ninja drop-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.35,0:01:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哦哟\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}My sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我的孩子们\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Ah, My sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.51,0:01:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,要成为真正的忍者\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}If you are to become true ninja,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.76,0:01:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你们必须更加努力\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}you must work harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.11,0:01:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的人生道路不会轻松\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Your path in life will not be an easy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.62,0:01:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,外面的世界对你们并不友好\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}The outside world will not be a friendly place for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.90,0:01:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你们四个如此与众不同\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You four are different in ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,地上的人们不会理解的\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}the surface dwellers would never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,为了生存\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}To survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你们必须掌握我教的这些技巧\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}you must master these skills I teach you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,忍术中的潜行与隐遁之术\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}ninjitsu powers of stealth and secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你们必须成为影丸 影子武士\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You must become kage, shadow warriors,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:01:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,绝不能被外界所察觉\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}and you must never be discovered by the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯? 那是什么声音\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Eh? What is that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哇! 地震了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Whoa! Earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在纽约?\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}In New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,有这个可能 但几率不大\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Possible, but not likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那些是什么东西\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}What are those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,纽约的蟑螂吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}New York City cockroaches?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是什么东西\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Whatever they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,它们来错地方了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}they picked the wrong party to crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 李奥\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Hey, Leo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,快速出击\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}think fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得帮帮斯普林特老师\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We have to help Master Splinter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,快来\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,小心\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 不\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,斯普林特老师\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Master Splinter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,斯普林特老师\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Master Splinter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,斯普林特老师\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Master Splinter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}No!
